  "description": "<p>Tired of the whole layering thing? Designed for adventure hungry skiers, climbers and hikers, the Couloir Insulated Jacket uses breathable Primaloft Gold insulation where you need it, while still allowing free flowing mobility. The three-layer GORE-TEX\u00ae fabric provides optimal breathability when you are plugging hard for the summit, and protection when conditions take a turn on the descent. A helmet-compatible hood and high pockets that accommodate a harness or hipbelt are ideal for high mountain endeavors. From powder smashing to spring alpine pursuits, one jacket has you covered you this season.</p><ul><li>2-layer recycled nylon shell with a GORE-TEX\u00ae membrane and DWR finish for superior waterproofness and breathability</li><li>GORE-TEX C-Knit\u2122 lining slides easily over other layers and reduces weight while adding breathability</li><li>Breathable Primaloft Gold synthetic insulation is body-mapped for warmth in the torso and mobility in the sleeves and hood</li><li>Fully seam-taped construction keeps you dry in howling conditions</li><li>Helmet-compatible hood has embedded cordlock adjustments for a snag-free profile</li><li>Articulated arms and patterning ensure unrestricted movement</li><li>Large front pockets sit high for backpack and harness compatibility</li><li>Zippered chest pocket and internal oversized stow pockets store essentials</li><li>Underarm vents have 2-way zippers to release heat</li><li>Velcro\u00ae cuffs and shock-cord adjustable hem seals out snow and drafts</li><li>Contoured cuffs layer well with gloves</li><li>Built-in Recco\u00ae Rescue System reflector allows ski patrol and mountain rescue teams to detect and locate it under snow</li><li>Pairs perfectly with the Couloir Gore-Tex Bib Pants for a backcountry-ready system</li></ul>",
